\pard\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0\f0\fs36 Q.2 Describe css selectors and list the tyepes  of selectors (e.g., element ,class,id).\par

\pard\sb100\sa100\sl240\slmult1\f1 Anser :\b\fs24  CSS Selectors\b0  are patterns used to \b select and style HTML elements\b0  on a webpage.\line They tell the browser \b which element(s)\b0  the CSS rules should apply to.\par

\pard\sa160\sl259\slmult0\f0\fs36 p \{\par
  color: red;\par
\}\par
\fs22 Here, \f2\fs20 p\f0\fs22  is a selector that targets all \f2\fs20 <p>\f0\fs22  (paragraph) elements and sets their text color to red.\par

